gods.description: Recent nerfs to Warrior's Blessing have helped to bring about an influx of mages and guardians to the solo lane.  If you find yourself laning against a magical opponent, choosing to build a magical defense item like Runic Shield or Genji's Guard, before going into physical resistance, may be preferable to standard builds.
